column2: SELECT TOP # Q.BestObjID, u, g, Q.ra, Q.dec, Q.z, G.ObjID, G.ra, G.dec, G.z N.distance  From Galaxy as G,   SpecObj as Q,   Neighbors as N,   SpecObj as S  WHERE Q.BestObjID = S.BestObjID   and Q.z > #  and Q.z < #  and u < #  and g <#  and Q.class in (&&&, &&&)   and G.ObjID = N.ObjID   and Q.BestObjID = N.NeighborObjID   and N.distance < #/#
